pe=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-474e3986\" data-id=\"474e3986\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2cff2272 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2cff2272\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<strong>PROPERTIES BY PATRICE<\/strong>\n<br><br>\nPatrice is a Realtor\u00ae and Senior Real Estate Specialist that approaches work with enthusiasm, creativity and a meticulous attention to detail.\u00a0\u00a0She is\u00a0a team player who uses her listening skills, strong work ethic, professionalism, negotiation abilities and positive attitude to achieve the required results in the selling and\/or buying of one\u2019s home.\n<br><br>\nBeing a University of Texas graduate, and having lived numerous places in the Austin area for over 2 decades, Patrice is knowledgeable of the surrounding areas, local events, and many activities.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0Patrice has found that her greatest professional and personal successes is in assembling strong relationships, as she focuses on giving her best in every endeavor to surpass other\u2019s expectations.\u00a0\u00a0Her approach is centered around a \u201cclient-first\u201d philosophy to encourage and deliver a sense of deep satisfaction.\n<br><br>\nWhen not working with clients and friends, Patrice and her husband enjoy entertaining, cruising the lake, hiking, and traveling to new places to explore and experience new adventures.\u00a0\u00a0Patrice believes in giving back to the community, and she volunteers for many non-profit fundraising arenas including Austin Smiles; \u00a0Austin Loaves and Fishes; Crisis Pregnancy Center; \u00a0Colton\u2019s Hope; Suicide Awareness &amp; Project SemiColon.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0In addition, she supports numerous local art fundraisers and countless music events.\n<br><br>\nPatrice\u2019s desire and goal is to make the entire real estate process stress free, because having not only lived in Texas and several states, she has also lived in Italy and Canada, and knows from personal experience the pressures that moving can bring. \u00a0\u00a0She finds there is no better measure of success than the happiness and satisfaction to her clients, friends and family.\n<br><br>\n<a href=\"http:\/\/www.PropertiesByPatrice.com\">www.PropertiesByPatrice.com<\/a>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4944be00 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"4944be00\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<style>\n.elementor-column.elementor-col-33 ul.elementor-icon-list-items {\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n}    \n<\/style>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Our Agents Patrice Emrie Sales Associate Contact Mobile PROPERTIES BY PATRICE Patrice is a Realtor\u00ae and Senior Real Estate Specialist that approaches work with enthusiasm, creativity and a meticulous attention to detail.\u00a0\u00a0She is\u00a0a team player who uses her listening skills, strong work ethic, professionalism, negotiation abilities and positive attitude to achieve the required results in [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"element